snippet.title: Minecraft: Xbox One Edition Trailer
snippet.description: Minecraft, one of the best-selling games on Xbox 360, is now available on Xbox One. Create and explore your very own world where the only limit is what you can imagine—just be sure to build a shelter when night comes to stay safe from monsters.
